{"title_page": "Apink discography", "text_new": "{{More citations needed|date=March 2015}}\n{{Use mdy dates|date=November 2014}}\n{{Infobox artist discography\n| Artist        = [[Apink]]\n| Image         = A Pink at 2014 Seoul Music Awards, 23 January 2014 01.png\n| Caption       = Apink at 2014 Seoul Music Awards on January 23, 2014.\n| Alt           = \n| Studio        = 6\n| EP            = 8\n| Singles       = 29\n| Live          = 5\n| Compilation   = 3\n| Soundtrack    = 8\n| Video         = \n| Music videos  = 33\n| Option        = 7\n| Option name   = Collaborations\n| 1Option name  = Single albums\n| 1Option       = 1\n}}\n\nThe discography of South Korean girl group [[Apink]] consists of six [[studio album]]s, nine [[extended play]]s, three [[compilation album]]s, and twenty-nine [[Single (music)|singles]].\n\n== Albums ==\n===Studio albums===\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|+ List of studio albums, with selected details and chart positions\n! rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:10em;\" | Title\n! rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:20;\" | Album details\n! colspan=\"3\" scope=\"col\" | Peak chart positions\n! rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:12em;\" | Sales\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;font-size:90%;\"|[[Gaon Chart|KOR]]<br /><ref name=\"gaonalbum\">{{cite web|url=http://gaonchart.co.kr/chart/album.php |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150106234133/http://gaonchart.co.kr/chart/album.php |archivedate=January 6, 2015 |title=Gaon Weekly Album Chart |work=Gaon Chart |publisher=Korea Music Content Industry Association |language=ko |accessdate=August 24, 2014 |url-status=dead }}</ref>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;font-size:90%;\" | [[Oricon|JPN]]<br/><ref name=\"oricon-album\">{{cite web|title=Oricon Album Chart|url=https://www.oricon.co.jp/prof/540079/rank/album/|publisher=[[Oricon]]|language=ja|accessdate=June 18, 2018}}\n*{{cite web|url=https://www.oricon.co.jp/rank/ja/w/2015-08-03/p/4/|title=Pink Memory|date=August