m Nam-joo participated in this release but it was credited to Apink and [[Beast (South Korean band)|Beast]].}}\n| various artist\n|-\n|}\n\n== Videography ==\n===Video albums===\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:22em;\"| Title\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:20em;\"| Album details\n! scope=\"col\" colspan=\"1\" | Peak chart positions\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:8em;\"| Sales\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;font-size:90%;\"|[[Oricon|JPN]]<br><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.oricon.co.jp/prof/540079/rank/dvd/| title= Oricon - A Pink DVD Chart History|publisher=Oricon |accessdate=November 1, 2016|language=ja}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.oricon.co.jp/prof/540079/rank/blu-ray/| title= Oricon - A Pink Blu-ray Chart History|publisher=Oricon |accessdate=November 1, 2016|language=ja}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" |''APINK 1st Concert\u300cPINK PARADISE\u300dDVD''\n|\n* Released: June 24, 2015 {{small|(JPN)}}\n* Labels: Copan Global\n* Format: DVD\n| 22\n|\n*JPN: 2,302<ref name=\"oricon_sales\"/>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" |''Apink 1st Live Tour 2015 \uff5ePINK SEASON\uff5e''\n|\n* Released: February 10, 2016 {{small|(JPN)}}\n* Labels: Universal Music Japan\n* Format: DVD, Blu-ray\n| 17 {{small|(DVD)}}<br />11 {{small|(Blu-ray)}}\n|\n*JPN: 4,240<!--2,154(DVD) + 2,086(Blu-ray)--><ref name=\"oricon_sales\"/>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" |''APINK 2nd Concert Pink Island In Seoul''\n|\n* Released: March 9, 2016 {{small|(JPN)}}\n* Labels: Universal Music Japan\n* Format: DVD\n| 23\n|\n*JPN: 1,112<ref name=\"oricon_sales\"/>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" |''Apink 2nd Live Tour 2016 \u300cPINK SUMMER\u300d''\n|\n* Released: October 16, 2016 {{small|(JPN)}}\n* Labels: Universal Music Japan\n* Format: DVD, Blu-ray\n| 27 {{small|(DVD)}}<br />36 {{small|(Blu-ray)}}\n|\n*JPN: 2,763<ref>{{cite web |url=http://theqoo.net/index.php?mid=japan&category=26063&document_srl=350553771 |title=2